      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ沖縄に出発するのね",
      "startTime": 2.8666666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これから空港に向かって約三時間で到着の予定です\n……遙子さん、緊張してるんですか？",
      "startTime": 10.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.466666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、沖縄に行くのはあの日以来だから……",
      "startTime": 14.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私と沖縄に行った時のこと\n{user}君は覚えてる？",
      "startTime": 21.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "覚えてますよ。遙子さんが沖縄で\n初ライブをすることになって俺も同行したんですよね",
      "startTime": 26.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.166666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも初めての沖縄だったから\n凄く緊張していたのよね",
      "startTime": 33.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに当時の俺は自分のことで手一杯で\n遙子さんが緊張していたことに気付かなくて",
      "startTime": 41.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃から遙子さんはおっとり……\n落ち着いて見えましたから",
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "今おっとりしてるって言おうとした？",
      "startTime": 49.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん今なら遙子さんが緊張してると分かりますよ\n意外と慌てん坊で実は涙もろいことも知ってます",
      "startTime": 56.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、付き合いが長いのも考えものだわ……",
      "startTime": 61.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 66.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの続きだけどね\nあの時は私も初めての沖縄で舞い上がってたのよ",
      "startTime": 70.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "絶対にライブで失敗出来ないと思って\n足が震えるくらい緊張しながら舞台に立ったのに……",
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの出番になった途端\n急に天気が荒れ始めたんですよね",
      "startTime": 85.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "土砂降りの雨でお客さんがみんな避難する中\n歌い始めていた私はステージを中断出来なくて……",
      "startTime": 92.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ずぶ濡れになりながら\n誰も居ない客席に向かって最後まで歌ったのよ",
      "startTime": 99.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あの後、遙子さんは相当落ち込んでましたね",
      "startTime": 103.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "だって、あの時思っちゃったんだもん\n雨が降ったのは私に運が無かったからだって……",
      "startTime": 111.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "もしも歌っていたのが麻奈ちゃんだったら\nきっと雨は降らなかったはずだって……",
      "startTime": 120.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんが雨の日に野外ライブをした話は\n{user}君も知ってるでしょ？",
      "startTime": 126.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。その場には俺もいましたから",
      "startTime": 128.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "野外ライブ当日に雨が降って\nライブは中止になると誰もが思っていた時に",
      "startTime": 135.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "雨の中、麻奈ちゃんが野外ステージに飛び出して\n『星の海の記憶』を歌い出したの",
      "startTime": 143.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "するとさっきまで降っていた雨が嘘みたいに晴れて\n満点の星空の下でライブは大成功に終わった……",
      "startTime": 151.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "私の沖縄初ライブが雨で台無しになった時\nそのエピソードを思い出して落ち込んだわ",
      "startTime": 160.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "これが持ってる人とそうじゃない人の差なんだって\n思い知らされた気がしたから",
      "startTime": 167.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "考え過ぎですよ。あれは偶然です\nいくら麻奈でも天気までは変えられません",
      "startTime": 173.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるけど、考えずにはいられないの",
      "startTime": 176.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄のライブで雨が降ったのは、麻奈ちゃんと違って\n私が持っていない人間だからなんだって……",
      "startTime": 185.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "それでずーんって落ち込んでたら\n{user}君が提案してくれたのよね",
      "startTime": 192.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "来年沖縄で行われる野外ライブイベントに\nエントリーしてみないかって",
      "startTime": 198.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄でライブを成功させれば\n遙子さんは嫌な思い出を払拭出来ると思ったんです",
      "startTime": 203.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "提案された時は驚いたわ～",
      "startTime": 207.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺がイベントの参加を勧めるのはそんなに変ですか？",
      "startTime": 210,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうよ！　だってあの頃は\n麻奈ちゃんに付きっきりだったんだもーん",
      "startTime": 217.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "私のことなんて気にしてないと思ってたから\n寄り添って考えてくれたのが意外で、嬉しかった",
      "startTime": 223.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}君を信じて\n翌年の野外イベントに挑戦することにしたのよ",
      "startTime": 230.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、翌年は台風が直撃してイベント中止……\nほんと、私って運が無いのよね～",
      "startTime": 240.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで、どんなに頑張っても麻奈ちゃんみたいには\nなれないんだって思い知らされちゃった",
      "startTime": 248.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈のようになる必要はありませんよ\n遙子さんには遙子さんの魅力があるんですから",
      "startTime": 255.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、遙子さんは『持ってる人』です\n間近で見てきた俺が言うんですから信じて下さい",
      "startTime": 262.1666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk029.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\nそう言ってもらえて少し元気が出たわ",
      "startTime": 268.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに向けて出来ることがあれば何でも言って下さい\n遙子さんが元気になるなら何だってしますから",
      "startTime": 275.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk030.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、私が頑張ったらご褒美をくれる？",
      "startTime": 279.46666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "いいですよ\n頑張ったご褒美に遙子さんの頼みを何でも聞きます",
      "startTime": 285.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk031.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄で行きたい所があるんだけど\n連れて行ってもらえる？",
      "startTime": 291.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。ライブが終わったら\n遙子さんの好きな所へ連れて行きます",
      "startTime": 296.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk032.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ廃墟がいいわ！\nずっと見たかったいい廃墟が沖縄にあるのよ～！",
      "startTime": 301.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "え……せっかく沖縄にまで行って廃墟じゃなくても……",
      "startTime": 305.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_01-hrk033.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、俄然やる気が出てきたわ！\nライブ、楽しみにしていてね",
      "startTime": 315.03333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    }
